<DOCID> 273542 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
September 9, 1990, Sunday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Sports; Part C; Page 2; Column 1; Sports Desk 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
<P>
544 words 
</P>
