Larry Jon Hobbs, educator 
</P>
<P>
Tony Vasquez, community planner/educator 
</P>
<P>
Kelly Olsen, writer 
</P>
<P>
Kathleen Schwallie, attorney 
</P>
<P>
Donna Alvarez, retired businesswoman 
</P>
<P>
Christine Emerson Reed, incumbent City Council member 
</P>
