<P>
Photo, Johnathan Arrington ; Photo, Johnathan Arrington shows off several of 
the trophies that his son, Jonathan, has earned. DAVID McNEW / Los Angeles 
Times; Photo, Close companions, from left, Jonathan Arrington, 19, Khalil 
Mohammed, 17, and Hubert Phillips, 19, excelled together on the football field 
at Southwest High School, which they all attended. Phillips had won a football 
scholarship. 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
