<HEADLINE>
<P>
ORANGE COUNTY NEWSMAKERS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
* Greg Winner has been named vice president of design engineering for Silicon 
Systems, a Tustin-based manufacturer of semiconductors. In his new position, 
Winner will lead product-development activities at the company's Tustin Design 
Center. Winner, who joined the company in 1982, was previously director of 
design engineering. 
