<P>
* Henry J. Todd has been named vice president and general manager of the 
product support division at McDonnell Douglas Space Systems Co. in Huntington 
Beach. 
</P>
<P>
He was previously vice president and general manager of the firm's quality 
systems division. Bonnie W. Soodik was named the new general manager of the 
quality systems division. Soodik joined McDonnell Douglas Automation Co. in 
1977, then moved to Douglas Aircraft Co. in 1987 as program manager for 
information resource management. 
</P>
