<HEADLINE>
<P>
ON THE RECORD 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
"To date, no one has ever served a day in jail for payola." 
</P>
<P>
 -- Fredrick Dannen, author of "Hit Men," which details promotion methods in 
the recording industry, after a federal judge last week dismissed the biggest 
music payola and rackeetering trial in 30 years. 
</P>
</TEXT>
