<P>
LONG BEACH OFFICE TOPS IN CENTURY 21 REGION 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Century 21 A Marketplace, 1650 Ximeno Ave., Long Beach, was named top producing 
office in the Los Angeles district of Century 21 of the Pacific. In July, the 
office closed more than $12.3 million in real estate sales. 
</P>
<P>
David Carden received the coveted President's pin for outstanding sales 
production and Carl Proctor, also of Century 21 A Marketplace, was cited among 
the top agents for the Los Angeles/South Bay area. 
</P>
