<HEADLINE>
<P>
DESIGNERS TO HONOR GETTY ART CURATOR 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Gillian Wilson, curator of decorative arts at the J. Paul Getty Museum, has 
been selected by the California Los Angeles chapter of the American Society of 
Interior Designers as the 1990 recipient of its prestigious Crystal Torch 
Award. 
</P>
<P>
Wilson will be honored today at the fourth annual Crystal Torch Award luncheon 
in the Crystal Room of the Beverly Hills Hotel. Event proceeds benefit the 
Foundation for Interior Design Education Research. 
</P>
</TEXT>
